# NoneBot-Adapter-Gewechat

_✨ NoneBot2 Gewechat Protocol适配器 / Gewechat Protocol Adapter for NoneBot2 ✨_

<a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Shine-Light/nonebot-adapter-gewechat@master/LICENSE">
